WEBVTT 

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:03.760
I participated in many protests.

00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:08.720
We also made a video
where I was speaking

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.440
next to the governor of the region.

00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:17.400
I said they have to stop
bringing waste to our town,

00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:22.240
so that children and adults
would not get sick

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:25.640
and people could breathe clean air.

00:00:25.720 --> 00:00:28.440
Before, it didn't smell
and people moved here

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:30.760
but now people are moving away.

